task: Turn wifi on through the settings app.

action.description: Launch the Settings app.
Tap on the "Network & internet" option to proceed to Wi-Fi settings.
Tap on the "Internet" option to proceed to Wi-Fi settings.
Tap the Wi-Fi toggle switch to turn on Wi-Fi.
